name: AJP

projects.title: NibbleAt
projects.description: NibbleAt is localized food recommendation engine with discounts, deals, and promotions. Built using React Native!

projects.title: StreamShip
projects.description: StreamShip is a streaming site aggregator that includes the IMDB, Rotten Tomatoes, and Metacritic score for movies that are available.  Written in Python the movie data was scraped off of Netflix in 2020.

projects.title: AutoSupreme
projects.description: AutoSupreme is a chrome extension that allows you to checkout of the popular lifestyle brand online store with a single click. AutoSupreme currently has over 2,500 unique downloads in over 30 different countries.

projects.title: WhoU
projects.description: WhoU is an eBusiness card, users can exchange phone numbers, Snapchat, Instagram and Twitter accounts with a click of a button. Built with Swift!

aboutpara: I grew up in New Hampshire and went to Arizona State University to study Computer Science. I am currently working remote for American Express as a backend engineer for their mobile app, as well as a Software Consultant.
